CraftClass is an unofficial fan tool for Path of Exile 2. Path of Exile 2 and
all related game content are trademarks of Grinding Gear Games. CraftClass
is not affiliated with or endorsed by Grinding Gear Games.

Item data is sourced from poe2db.tw (CC BY-NC-SA) and game files via
SnosMe's poe-dat-viewer (MIT). Currency prices are fetched from poe2.ninja /
poe2scout.com. We are grateful to these projects and the Path of Exile 2
community for making this tool possible.